 the XY-model in a transverse field to which our model is dual.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2011 21:30:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Jan 2012 19:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-17"}
