alues for directions longitudinal and\ntransverse to the bulk (driving) flow. Thus, the intensity fluctuations of the\nQP exhibit statistical properties consistent with an underling turbulent flow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2011 09:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2012 14:20:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-30"}
