 main strengths of the\nproposed theory are its generality and direct microscopic connection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2011 10:13:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Feb 2013 19:08:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-26"}
